  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Heave Ho is a riotous multiplayer party game for up to four players in couch co-op and versus play, or online with Steam Remote Play. Reach out, get a grip, and swing to victory — or meet your messy end!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/905340/extras/d602e7c5cf98a9e0859455d0833a8e70.avif?t=1772546938\" width=615 height=131 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Reach out</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can your team of up to four players swing to victory? It’s all or nothing — the slightest slip sends your fellow Heavers to their technicolor deaths in the void or on the spikes. It’s a fast-track to ruined friendships.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/905340/extras/ea1d9109610772b2d32223c2ddd9fef1.webp?t=1772546938\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/905340/extras/ea1d9109610772b2d32223c2ddd9fef1.poster.webp?t=1772546938\" class=\"bb_img\" width=615 height=279 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Get a grip</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s simple — grab pals and platforms with your hands, form a wobbly chain, and swing across increasingly devilish maps without letting go or missing your mark. I mean, how hard can it be?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/905340/extras/5ff1646f742e5d0fd8da4edf46422d51.webp?t=1772546938\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/905340/extras/5ff1646f742e5d0fd8da4edf46422d51.poster.webp?t=1772546938\" class=\"bb_img\" width=615 height=279 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pimp your Swingers</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your base character and customize them with a range of dashing accessories, none of which do anything to help you avoid the plummet of doom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/905340/extras/9337e243e6305868c7d9a881b6fc8622.webp?t=1772546938\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/905340/extras/9337e243e6305868c7d9a881b6fc8622.poster.webp?t=1772546938\" class=\"bb_img\" width=615 height=279 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Heave Versus Ho</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you can no longer handle your useless co-op teammates letting you down — literally — then take a swing at the 20 exclusive versus mode levels and teach them a lesson.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/905340/extras/690fac8eaed67743015e890e5cd96b8b.webp?t=1772546938\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/905340/extras/690fac8eaed67743015e890e5cd96b8b.poster.webp?t=1772546938\" class=\"bb_img\" width=615 height=279 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Camel Farts</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Distractions come in all shapes and sizes, but this might be the first time impenetrable clouds of camel gas have conspired against you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/905340/extras/5c3ac565afeda4b03d07cb3da2375cb9.webp?t=1772546938\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/905340/extras/5c3ac565afeda4b03d07cb3da2375cb9.poster.webp?t=1772546938\" class=\"bb_img\" width=615 height=279 /></picture></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Heave Ho is a riotous multiplayer party game for up to four players in couch co-op and versus play, or online with Steam Remote Play. Reach out, get a grip, and swing to victory — or meet your messy end!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/905340/extras/d602e7c5cf98a9e0859455d0833a8e70.avif?t=1772546938\" width=615 height=131 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Reach out</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can your team of up to four players swing to victory? It’s all or nothing — the slightest slip sends your fellow Heavers to their technicolor deaths in the void or on the spikes. It’s a fast-track to ruined friendships.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/905340/extras/ea1d9109610772b2d32223c2ddd9fef1.webp?t=1772546938\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/905340/extras/ea1d9109610772b2d32223c2ddd9fef1.poster.webp?t=1772546938\" class=\"bb_img\" width=615 height=279 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Get a grip</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s simple — grab pals and platforms with your hands, form a wobbly chain, and swing across increasingly devilish maps without letting go or missing your mark. I mean, how hard can it be?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/905340/extras/5ff1646f742e5d0fd8da4edf46422d51.webp?t=1772546938\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/905340/extras/5ff1646f742e5d0fd8da4edf46422d51.poster.webp?t=1772546938\" class=\"bb_img\" width=615 height=279 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pimp your Swingers</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your base character 